{"tid":389561,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[冇圖]俾你揀會揀冠軍雷莊兜定民選票后張寶欣","createTime":"2017-09-06T11:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T17:40:25.000Z","uid":9564,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1052c57f57845dfaf864350a1c8fd04b89fb6f4d","tid":389561,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 民選票后張寶欣<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/190222_a319c86716790b0b20cd0ef73c2ec810.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F190222_a319c86716790b0b20cd0ef73c2ec810.jpg&h=9bf4745c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兜兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf5785a518ea8800453d7bd33e1cf7c209e5844","tid":389561,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:07:22.000Z","msg":"雖然寶欣入唔到三甲<br />\n但3分鐘內最少10萬香港人投票俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 民選冠軍是為實至名歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲勁撚過游B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e20a48161628a3c9c7cc5a1ef24af40311f8fe","tid":389561,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266ad3fffb6319d62b9e61e2c45540db0af0a927","tid":389561,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0fa93bdbf6d1284a76c4c8f672b662e72b3dec","tid":389561,"uid":92376,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:28:00.000Z","msg":"BBC最受歡迎香港小姐數據分析<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/024412_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F024412_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=257bb87e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據mytv個時間 17:42個陣10號個累積數量係704990<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/024504_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F024504_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=deb3a36e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n19:13個陣10號個累積數量係757943<br />\n<br />\n總時間長度=19:13-17:42=91秒<br />\n數量增長=757943-704990=52953<br />\n增長速率=52953/91=582/秒<br />\n<br />\n根據賽前BBC記錄 10號同9號有明顯差距<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/024922_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F024922_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c861a540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10號同9號差距=1768205-698644=1069561<br />\n<br />\n假設10號一直保持同一個速率去追<br />\n假設9號當晚完全冇增長<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">10號超越9號所需時間=1069561/582=1838秒=31分鐘</span><br />\n<br />\n成個環節頭尾應該冇30分鐘 仲要未計9號當晚個增長 <br />\n完全睇唔到10號會贏個可能性<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n----------------------<br />\n<strong>蘋果日報--【唔公平?】超專業分析 網友 : 最受歡迎港姐無可能係張寶欣</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://is.gd/bBrel3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FbBrel3&d=eN%2Foexm6BYkdW6HtB%2B3Tn7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=779e74a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/bBrel3</a><br />\n<br />\n今年香港小姐競選決賽不斷Hard Sell大台直播App，就連友誼小姐一獎都改做「big big channel最受歡迎香港小姐」。此獎項以直播App上網友給的心心作標準，稱以最高心心數量的佳麗奪得，最後獎項由10號張寶欣獲得。先不論有大量網友投訴直播App在比賽其間完全不能開啟，既然這麼多人未能連線，那心心從哪裡來可說是個迷。賽前被網友極力支持的9號金美黎，不但三甲不入，就連「BBC最受歡迎港姐」都拿不到令他們心心不忿。有網友製作圖表加上超專業的數據分析指出獎項根本不應由10號張寶欣獲得，獲獎的該是9號金美黎，指比賽有不公之嫌。 <br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀: <strong>香港01【港姐2017】張寶欣Big Big Channel心心疑造假　金美黎輸得唔抵</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/娛樂/116762/-港姐2017-張寶欣Big-Big-Channel心心疑造假-金美黎輸得唔抵\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F116762%2F-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A7%902017-%E5%BC%B5%E5%AF%B6%E6%AC%A3Big-Big-Channel%E5%BF%83%E5%BF%83%E7%96%91%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87-%E9%87%91%E7%BE%8E%E9%BB%8E%E8%BC%B8%E5%BE%97%E5%94%94%E6%8A%B5&d=eN%2Foexm6BYkdW6HtB%2B3Tn7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=dbecbf49\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/娛樂/116762/-港姐2017-張寶欣Big-Big-Channel心心疑造假-金美黎輸得唔抵</a><br />\n<br />\n今日追加: TVB高層余詠珊最權威回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>有網民質疑網上投票「最受歡迎香港小姐」，賽前是⑨金美黎累積最多心心，但最後是⑩張寶欣奪獎？余詠珊稱張寶欣賽前累積加臨場獲200多萬心心，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕對不能造假</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n嘩,真係好合理好公道喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不要問只要信,講咩就係咩架啦,你地邊個敢質疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n寶欣叻叻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/389286\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/389286</a><br />\n一人一信要求通訊局徹查big big channel最受歡迎香港小姐數據疑似造假事件</span>"},{"pid":"fe093a3c717d083ee00fec179791faada5b9f9c0","tid":389561,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:33:28.000Z","msg":"上面做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5822ebac3147a44b42b09fa010c29b3aff440cb","tid":389561,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T12:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24aa5440575da2ea2ab9549da979ce6b670db40e","tid":389561,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T16:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02628a980a95e09192208de4793a92d7cc0ba39a","tid":389561,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T17:40:25.000Z","msg":"睇當晚表現而定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}